    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she's been absolutely wonderful to own. It's in great shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years\u2014super reliable and drives like a dream! It's perfect for someone looking for a dependable car that still looks sharp on the road. I've taken care of all the basics, so it's ready for its next adventure with you. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
