    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L straight-six engine with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS high-pressure variable valve timing. This driver-focused example utilizes a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing limited-slip differential, providing exceptional tactile feedback and power delivery. The chassis has been proactively addressed with rear subframe reinforcement and upgraded trailing arm bushings to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads. Recent service includes a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment and a cooling system refresh. While the exterior displays minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain and suspension geometry remain dialed for precision. This is a high-performance machine optimized for the purist who values mechanical integrity and throttle response.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
