    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2017 Porsche Macan GTS in Volcano Grey Metallic offers a perfect blend of performance and utility. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish, though it shows minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with regular highway use. Inside, the Garnet Red leather interior is in impressive shape with no rips or stains, and the cabin remains a strictly smoke-free environment. Every feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the Bose surround sound system, is fully operational. Mechanically, this vehicle has been meticulously maintained with a complete service log available; the PDK transmission shifts seamlessly, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. The tires are Pirelli P-Zeros with approximately 70% tread remaining. It is a reliable, eye-catching daily driver that has been cared for with pride and is ready for its next owner.",
